
######################################
#  Adventuron                        #
######################################

loading_screen = loading_screen
// autorediscribe if locations/objects changes
redescribe = auto_beta

start_at = santa_cellar

######################################
#  Variables                         #
######################################

integers {
   day_spend_walls_enigma : integer "0";
}

######################################
#  Locations                         #
######################################

locations {

   bookshop : location "You are at the book shop." ;

   church : location "You are in front of the church. You can access the tower if you enter." ;

   church_tower : location "You are in the church's tower. Rumor has it that a secret bell combination will result in all nearby pigeons being reunited here. Enter RING NUMBER (e.g. RING 0) to try calling pigeons." ;

   coocoo_cafe : location "You are at the famous Coocoo Cafe, where there is always a variety of pigeons on the roof. Enter inside!" ;
   
   coocoo_inside : location "You are inside the Coocoo Cafe. There are no customers." ;

   montauk_beach : location "Montauk is the place where lovers like to meet." ;

   nicobar_park : location "You are in Nicobar Park." ;

   pigeon_fountain : location "You are in the Pigeon Fountain." ;

   pigeon_route : location "You are in the Life or Bread labyrinth game.\n\nMove once a day and get the bread before a week to survive or this tomb will be your tomb!" ;

   robin_room : location "You are in Robin's bedroom, checking that Larry's friend Columbia safely delivered Robin's present." ;

   santa_cellar : location "This is Santa's cellar, where you can find different potions to keep him cheerful and full of energy." ;

   south_park : location "You are in the South of Nicobar Park." ;

   walls_n: location "";
   walls_ns: location "";
   walls_nse: location "";
   walls_nsen: location "";
   walls_nsene: location "";
   walls_nsenee: location "";
   walls_nses: location "";
   walls_nsesn: location "";
   walls_nsesnn: location "";
   walls_nss: location "";
   walls_s: location "";
   walls_se: location "";
   walls_see: location "";
   walls_win: location "You arrived at the end! Congratulations!";
}

######################################
#  Connections                       #
######################################

connections {

   from, direction, to = [
   santa_cellar, southeast, nicobar_park,
   nicobar_park, north, montauk_beach,
   nicobar_park, west, coocoo_cafe,
   nicobar_park, south, south_park,
   coocoo_cafe, south, bookshop,
   coocoo_cafe, enter, coocoo_inside, 
   bookshop, east, south_park,
   nicobar_park, northeast, pigeon_fountain,
   south_park, south, church,
   church, enter, church_tower,
   montauk_beach, north, robin_room,
   nicobar_park, east, pigeon_route,

   pigeon_route, north_oneway, walls_n,
   walls_n, south_oneway, walls_ns,
   walls_ns, east_oneway, walls_nse,
   walls_nse, north_oneway, walls_nsen,
   walls_nsen, east_oneway, walls_nsene,
   walls_nsene, east_oneway, walls_nsenee,
   walls_nse, south_oneway, walls_nses,
   walls_nses, north_oneway, walls_nsesn,
   walls_ns, south_oneway, walls_nss,
   walls_nss, east_oneway, walls_see,
   pigeon_route, south_oneway, walls_s,
   walls_s, east_oneway, walls_se,
   walls_se, east_oneway, walls_see,
   walls_see, north_oneway, walls_nse,
   walls_nsesn, east_oneway, walls_win,
   walls_nsesn, north_oneway, walls_nsesnn,
   walls_nsesnn, east_oneway, walls_nsenee,
   walls_nsenee, south_oneway, walls_win,
   ]

}

######################################
#  Objects                           #
######################################

objects {

bin : scenery "a beautiful Art Deco bin" at = "coocoo_cafe";

bookshop_owner : scenery "the bookshop owner" at = "bookshop";

bread : object "a generous loaf of bread and other goodies";

coin : object "a coal coin" at = "montauk_beach" ;

dictionary : object "a Korean-English dictionary" ;

intro : scenery "yourself crying and knowing that all children will think they were bad this year and didn't deserve a present" at = "nicobar_park" ;

after_intro : scenery "the pigeons following Larry to distribute all the presents" ;

larry : scenery "Larry, the leader of the pack of pigeons" at = "montauk_beach";

helping_larry : scenery "Larry flying (but is it going away or coming back?)" ;

morehelping_larry : scenery "Larry" ;

flying_pigeon : scenery "a pigeon singing even though its beak is carrying a Sappy Meal bag: \' lovers meet in Montauk Beach, lalala \'" at = "nicobar_park";

new_pigeon : scenery "a pigeon singing even though its beak is carrying a dumbbell: \'Best carriers meet in Montauk Beach, lalala \'";

absent_pigeon : scenery "no birdy no cry (where could they all be?)" at = "church_tower" ;

gang_pigeon : scenery "the biggest group of pigeons you've ever seen in your entire life is gathered here" ;

pigeon_book : object "a book \'Pigeons love bread\'" at = "nicobar_park" ;

pigeon_bookreal : object "the real bible about pigeons \'Lovey Dovey Pigeons\'" ;

robin : scenery "Robin is happily screaming 'I can't wait to play Call Of Beauty!'" at = "robin_room" ;

tourist : scenery "a tourist" at = "church_tower";

happy_tourist : scenery "a tourist" ;

unpaid_tourguide : scenery "the tour guide for the Church Tower" at = "church"  ;

friendly_tourguide : scenery "the tour guide for the Church Tower" ;

waitress : scenery "a waitress from Coocoo Cafe. She looks very tired" at = "coocoo_inside" ;

grateful_waitress : scenery "The Coocoo Cafe team is grateful for your help. You got rid of all extra cookies and croissants...  But where?" ;

}

######################################
#  Barriers                          #
######################################

barriers {

   block_larry : block {

      location = robin_room
      message  = The path is blocked by Larry
      block_when_exists = larry

   }

   block_helpinglarry : block {

      location = robin_room
      message  = The path is blocked
      block_when_exists = helping_larry

   }

   block_tourguide : block {

      location = church_tower
      message  = The path is blocked the tour guide
      block_when_exists = unpaid_tourguide

   }

}

######################################
#  On Startup                        #
######################################

on_startup {

   : play_music sound="music_sleepy";
   : print "Type VERB NOUN with the keyboard to advance in the game." ;
   : print "e.g. EXAMINE PIGEON to take a closer look at a PIGEON." ;
   : print "GET BREAD to take BREAD and add it to your inventory." ;
   : press_any_key ;
   : print "To travel, type NORTH, EAST, SOUTH, WEST (or N, E, S, W)" ;
   : press_any_key ;
   : print "To check your inventory, type INVENTORY (or I, POCKETS)" ;
   : press_any_key ;
   : print "Christmas is coming tonight, everyone cannot wait to open presents. While you are organizing the distribution, all your reindeer suddenly become unable to move." ;
   : print "How will you find a way to send all presents in time for the big day?" ;
   : print "Press any key to continue." ;

   : press_any_key ;

}

######################################
#  On Describe                       #
######################################

on_describe {

   : if (is_present "unpaid_tourguide") {
      : print "The guide says, \"The entrance fee per day is 1 coal coin.\"." ;
   }

   : if (is_present "larry") {
      : print "Larry says, \"I'm glad you met me in Montauk. I hope you've not come empty-handed.\"." ;
   }

   : if (is_at "robin_room" ) {
      : print "CONGRATULATIONS !" ;
      : print "YOU WON THE GAME !" ;
      : print "THANKS TO YOU, ROBIN AND ALL KIDS AROUND THE WORLD WILL BE HAPPY ON CHRISTMAS!" ;
      : play_music sound="music_victory";
      : press_any_key ;
      : clear_screen;
      : stop_music;
      : win_game ;
   }
   : if (is_at "nicobar_park") {
       : stop_music;
   }
   : if (is_at "coocoo_inside" ) {
       : play_music sound="coocooca";
   }
   : if (is_at "bookshop" ) {
       : play_music sound="bookshop";
   }
   : if (is_at "church_tower" ) {
       : play_music sound="church";
   }
   : if (is_at "montauk_beach" ) {
       : play_music sound="larrybeach2";
   }
   : if (is_at "pigeon_route" ) {
       : play_music sound="music_labyrinth";
       : set_integer var = "day_spend_walls_enigma" value = "6";
   }
   : if (is_at "walls_s" ) {
       : add var = "day_spend_walls_enigma" value = "1" ;
   }
   : if (is_at "walls_nsen" ) {
       : add var = "day_spend_walls_enigma" value = "1" ;
   }
   : if (is_at "walls_nss" ) {
       : add var = "day_spend_walls_enigma" value = "2" ;
   }
   : if (is_at "walls_nsesnn" ) {
       : add var = "day_spend_walls_enigma" value = "2" ;
   }
   : if (is_at "walls_win" ) {
      : if (day_spend_walls_enigma == 6) {
            # should only show "Retry" phrase when object has not been won
            : print "You did it in the shortest time possible, you win fresh bread! \n\nRetry it taking the slowest path to get a consolation (=loser) prize.";
      }
      : else_if (day_spend_walls_enigma == 10) {
            # should only show "Retry" phrase when object has not been won
            : print "You did it in the longest time possible, you win stale bread!\n(and you kept your life YAY!)\n\nRetry it taking the least time possible whenever you want.";
      }
      : else {
            # should only show "Retry" phrase when object has not been won
            : print "You spent too much time and won NOTHING!\n(but you kept your life YAY!)\n\nRetry it taking even more time or taking the least possible time!";
      }
      : press_any_key ;
      : goto "nicobar_park";
      : stop_music;
      : redescribe;
   }
}

######################################
#  On Command                        #
######################################

on_command {

   : match "ring 143"  {
      : if (is_at "church_tower") {
         : swap o1 = "absent_pigeon"  o2 = "gang_pigeon" ;
      }
   }

   : match "get bag; take bag"  {
      : if (is_at "coocoo_cafe") {
         : print "Pigeons are too high, and you are not fit enough to get to the roof." ;
      }
      : if (is_at "nicobar_park") {
         : print "The pigeon is very high in the sky, and you cannot fly without a reindeer." ;
      }
   }

   : match "examine beach"  {
      : if (is_at "montauk_beach") {
         : print "The beach is quiet today." ;
      }
   }

   : match "check bin; examine bin"  {
      : if (is_at "coocoo_cafe") {
         : print "There is sometimes a loaf of bread inside the bin." ;
      }
   }

   : match "give bread"  {
      : if (is_present "larry" && is_carried "bread" ) {
         : print "Larry takes the loaf of bread and says. \"Alright, we'll help you distribute the presents. Let's gather the troops at the Church Tower!\" ";
         : destroy "bread" ;
         : swap o1 = "larry"  o2 = "helping_larry" ;
         : swap o1 = "intro"  o2 = "after_intro" ;
         : swap o1 = "flying_pigeon"  o2 = "new_pigeon" ;
         : set_graphic graphic = "montauk_beach_nopigeon"  target = "montauk_beach" ;
      }
   }

   : match "get bread; take bread"  {
      : if (is_at "coocoo_cafe" && has_not_created "bread" && is_exists "grateful_waitress") {
        : print "You take the loaf of bread and other delicacies from the bin." ;
        : pocket "bread";
      }
   }

   : match "examine book; read book; use book"  {
      : if (is_at "nicobar_park" && is_carried "pigeon_book") {
         : print "Inside it says \'Pigeons love carrying heavy objects, but need energy to do so.\'" ;
      }
      : if (is_carried "pigeon_bookreal") {
         : print "Inside it says \'A pigeon can fly up to 143 kilometers per hour. Just ask for Caballero.\'" ;
      }
      : if (is_at "bookshop" && is_carried "pigeon_book") {
         : print "Who would want to read such a tiny book anyway?" ;
      }
   }

   : match "get book; take book"  {
      : if (is_at "nicobar_park" && has_not_created "pigeon_book") {
        : print "You take the book" ;
        : pocket "pigeon_book";
      }
   }

   : match "clean cafe; tidy cafe"  {
      : if (is_present "waitress") {
         : print "You are helping the Coocoo Cafe team.";
         : swap o1 = "waitress"  o2 = "grateful_waitress" ;
         ;
      }
   }

   : match "examine cafe"  {
      : if (is_at "coocoo_cafe") {
         : print "The Coocoo Cafe is about to close, but there is so much left to do!" ;
      }
   }

   : match "examine children"  {
      : if (is_at "nicobar_park") {
         : print "You are the only child here." ;
      }
   }


   : match "examine church"  {
      : if (is_at "church") {
         : print "This church looks like it's from the Victorian era." ;
      }
   }

   : match "examine coal; examine coin"  {
      : if (is_at "montauk_beach") {
         : print "This coin could be useful." ;
      }
   }

   : match "get coal; take coal; get coin; take coin"  {
      : if (is_at "montauk_beach" && has_not_created "coin") {
        : print "You take the coal coin. People throw anything away these days." ;
        : pocket "coin";
      }
   }

   : match "give coin; give coal"  {
      : if (is_present "unpaid_tourguide" && is_carried "coin") {
         : print "The tour guide gladly takes the coin and says \"Great, let's visit the Church Tower! Please come in!\" ";
         : destroy "coin" ;
         : swap o1 = "unpaid_tourguide"  o2 = "friendly_tourguide" ;
      }
   }

   : match "examine coocoo"  {
      : if (is_at "coocoo_cafe") {
         : print "The Coocoo Cafe is about to close, but there is so much left to do!" ;
      }
   }
   
   : match "clean coocoo; tidy coocoo"  {
      : if (is_present "waitress") {
         : print "You are helping the Coocoo Cafe team.";
         : swap o1 = "waitress"  o2 = "grateful_waitress" ;
         ;
      }
   }

   : match "use dictionary; read dictionary"  {
      : if (is_present "tourist" && is_carried "dictionary") {
         : print "The tourist laughs \"Oh you don't speak Korean? Dear me! You should have said so! I was meditating over this book. Oh, I have an English version as well. Please take it.\". He gives you the book. ";
         : create "pigeon_bookreal" ;
         : pocket "pigeon_bookreal" ;
         : swap o1 = "tourist"  o2 = "happy_tourist" ;
      }
   }

: match "examine guide; talk guide; examine tour; talk tour; examine tourguide; talk tourguide"  {
      : if (is_present "unpaid_tourguide") {
         : clear_screen;
         : print "\"No coin? Go home\", says the poetic tourguide." ;
         : press_any_key ;
         : redescribe;
      }
      : if (is_present "friendly_tourguide") {
         : print "\"Welcome! Come in!\", says the happy tourguide." ;
      }
   }

   : match "get larry; take larry"  {
      : if (is_at "montauk_beach") {
         : print "Pigeons are not pocket monsters, you cannot just catch them." ;
      }
   }

   : match "examine larry; talk larry"  {
      : if (is_present "larry") {
         : clear_screen;
         : print "\"Can't you see we are all hungry?\", says Larry." ;
         : press_any_key ;
         : redescribe;
      }
      : if (is_present "helping_larry" && is_exists "absent_pigeon") {
         : print "Larry has gone to organize everything." ;
      }
      : if (is_present "helping_larry" && is_exists "gang_pigeon") {
         : clear_screen;
         : print "\"Okay, everything should go well now. We're almost done.\", says Larry." ;
         : swap o1 = "helping_larry"  o2 = "morehelping_larry" ;
         : press_any_key ;
         : redescribe;
      }
   }

   : match "examine lovers"  {
      : if (is_at "montauk_beach") {
         : print "You see pigeons making a heart shape in the sky." ;
      }
      : if (is_at "nicobar_park") {
         : print "You are alone here." ;
      }
   }

   : match "get meal; take meal"  {
      : if (is_at "coocoo_cafe") {
         : print "Pigeons are too high, and you are not fit enough to get to the roof." ;
      }
      : if (is_at "nicobar_park") {
         : print "The pigeon is very high in the sky, and you cannot fly without a reindeer." ;
      }
   }

   : match "examine montauk"  {
      : if (is_at "montauk_beach") {
         : print "The beach is quiet today." ;
      }
   }

   : match "examine owner; talk owner; examine vendor; talk vendor"  {
      : if (is_present "bookshop_owner") {
         : clear_screen;
         : print "\"안녕하세요! \", says the bookshop owner. Maybe you will need to translate to English." ;
         : press_any_key ;
         : redescribe;
      }
   }

   : match "translate owner; talk english; translate english; translate _"  {
      : if (is_present "bookshop_owner") {
         : clear_screen;
         : print "\"Oh you don't speak Korean? Dear me! Everyone needs a Korean-English dictionary in their life. You can get one by exchanging with another book.\"" ;
         : press_any_key ;
         : redescribe;
      }
   }

   : match "give book; exchange book"  {
      : if (is_present "bookshop_owner" && is_carried "pigeon_book") {
            : print "\"Thank you! 'Tis the season to be jolly and enlighten your spirits with this piece of literature. It will open a new world to you.\" You get a Korean-English dictionary." ;
            : destroy "pigeon_book" ;
            : create "dictionary" ;
            : pocket "dictionary" ;
      }
      : if (is_present "bookshop_owner" && is_carried "pigeon_bookreal") {
            : print "\"This book has a Not For Sale Specimen stamp on it. Sorry, we cannot take it.\" " ;
      }
   }

   : match "give dictionary; exchange dictionary"  {
         : if (is_present "bookshop_owner" && is_carried "dictionary") {
            : print "\"We do not accept returns.\" " ;
      }
   }

   : match "examine park"  {
      : if (is_at "nicobar_park") {
         : print "You are alone, there is nothing to do here and it's raining." ;
      }
   }

   : match "examine pigeon; examine pigeons"  {
      : if (is_at "coocoo_cafe") {
         : print "You see pigeons eating and flying with colorful doggy bags. It's like a very busy restaurant." ;
      }
      : if (is_at "montauk_beach") {
         : print "Pigeons are flying, exercising and eating. Very healthy." ;
      }
      : if (is_at "nicobar_park") {
         : print "The pigeon looks happy and busy." ;
      }
      : if (is_at "church_tower") {
         : print "The pigeons are getting ready for a big mission." ;
      }
   }

   : match "get pigeon; take pigeon; talk pigeon"  {
      : if (is_at "coocoo_cafe") {
         : print "Pigeons are too high, and you are not fit enough to get to the roof." ;
      }
      : if (is_at "montauk_beach") {
         : print "Pigeons are not pocket monsters, you cannot just catch them." ;
      }
      : if (is_at "nicobar_park") {
         : print "The pigeon is very high in the sky, and you cannot fly without a reindeer." ;
      }
      : if (is_present "larry") {
         : clear_screen;
         : print "\"Can't you see we are all hungry?\", says Larry." ;
         : press_any_key ;
         : redescribe;
      }
   }

   : match "examine potion; examine potions; get potion; get potions; examine cellar"  {
      : if (is_at "santa_cellar") {
         : print "These potions are only for Santa, giving him strength for Christmas day." ;
      }
   }

   : match "examine present"  {
      : if (is_at "nicobar_park") {
         : print "There are no presents here." ;
      }
   }

   : match "examine reindeer; examine reindeers"  {
      : if (is_at "santa_cellar") {
         : print "It seems that Santa's potions only work on Santa. The reindeers are all incapable of moving!" ;
      }
   }

   : match "examine roof"  {
      : if (is_at "coocoo_cafe") {
         : print "You see pigeons eating and flying with colorful doggy bags. It's like a very busy restaurant." ;
      }
   }

   : match "examine shop"  {
      : if (is_at "bookshop") {
         : print "This is an exchange only bookshop. Books are the currency." ;
      }
   }

   : match "examine tourist; talk tourist; examine visitor; talk visitor"  {
      : if (is_present "tourist") {
         : clear_screen;
         : print "\"나는 비둘기를 위해 여기에 왔습니다! '비둘기 집에 음식을 두면 비둘기가 옵니다'\", says the cheerful tourist. Maybe you will need to use another item to have a fruitful conversation." ;
         : press_any_key ;
         : redescribe;
      }
      : if (is_present "happy_tourist") {
         : print "\"It doesn't matter what people call you unless they call you pigeon pie and eat you up.\", says the happy tourist." ;
      }
   }

   : match "help waitress"  {
      : if (is_present "waitress") {
         : print "You are helping the Coocoo Cafe team.";
         : swap o1 = "waitress"  o2 = "grateful_waitress" ;
         ;
      }
   }

: match "examine waitress; talk waitress"  {
      : if (is_present "waitress") {
         : clear_screen;
         : print "\"There is so much work!!!! Please help me\", says the desperate waitress." ;
         : press_any_key ;
         : redescribe;
      }
   }

   : match "look yourself; talk yourself"  {
      : if (is_at "nicobar_park") {
         : print "You are alone, there is nothing to do here and it's raining." ;
      }
   }

}

assets {
   sounds {
      music_victory : sound_sample "https://ea.gizal.org/okfeather/coocoo_cafe.mp3" ;
      music_labyrinth : sound_sample "https://ea.gizal.org/okfeather/feathery_christmas/labyrinth1.mp3" ;
      music_sleepy : sound_sample "https://ea.gizal.org/okfeather/feathery_christmas/sleepy.mp3" ;
      music_church : sound_sample "https://ea.gizal.org/okfeather/feathery_christmas/church.mp3" ;
      music_bookshop : sound_sample "https://ea.gizal.org/okfeather/feathery_christmas/bookshop.mp3" ;
      music_larrybeach : sound_sample "https://ea.gizal.org/okfeather/feathery_christmas/larrybeach2.mp3" ;
      music_coocooca : sound_sample "https://ea.gizal.org/okfeather/feathery_christmas/coocooca.mp3" ;
   }
   graphics {
      coocoo_cafe    : base64_png "";
      loading_screen : base64_png "";
      montauk_beach : base64_png "";
      montauk_beach_nopigeon : base64_png "";
      nicobar_park   : base64_png "";
      robin_room     : base64_png "";
walls_nsesn : base64_png "";
walls_nsesnn : base64_png "";
walls_n : base64_png "";
walls_ns : base64_png "";
walls_s : base64_png "";
walls_nss : base64_png "";
walls_nse : base64_png "";
walls_win : base64_png "";
walls_nsene : base64_png "";
walls_see : base64_png "";
walls_nsen : base64_png "";
walls_nsenee : base64_png "";
walls_nses : base64_png "";
walls_se : base64_png "";
pigeon_route : base64_png "";
   }
}
